description:
This is a 44 minute workout called '45-minute NO REPEAT Full Body Strength Training' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Strength.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

45 MINUTE FULL BODY STRENGTH WORKOUT STRUCTURE AND EXERCISES
